    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-02-26</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-04-15T17:17:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>National Evaluation of Aviation and Aerospace Solutions to Climate Change Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation to seek to enter into an agreement with the National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine under which it must conduct a study on climate change mitigation efforts related to the civil aviation and aerospace industries, including developing and applying an appropriate indicator for assessing the effectiveness of such efforts.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
